  "detailed_description": "Classic literature meets classic gaming in Jane Austen's 8-bit Adventure! This 2D platformer stars Jane Austen, English novelist, who finds herself in an 8-bit video game. This game was developed to run on real NES hardware from the 1980s. The Steam release brings this retro experience to modern devices!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Battle characters from Jane Austen's novels!<br></li><li>Explore 8-bit England!<br></li><li>Defeat enemies with a quill!<br></li><li>Restore Miss Austen's books to the 8-bit library!<br></li><li>NES ROM file included!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377660/extras/2631d49d0c373eb13a11c8c012d02bf1.poster.avif?t=1705411004\" width=512 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377660/extras/2631d49d0c373eb13a11c8c012d02bf1.webm?t=1705411004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377660/extras/2631d49d0c373eb13a11c8c012d02bf1.mp4?t=1705411004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
